287
00:16:02,756 --> 00:16:05,156
Hei, Conan!

288
00:16:05,156 --> 00:16:06,356
Ini dia.

289
00:16:06,356 --> 00:16:08,056
Aku mengumpulkannya dan menyatukannya kembali

290
00:16:08,056 --> 00:16:10,356
dan itu menjadi satu blok bata.

291
00:16:11,356 --> 00:16:13,356
Ini...

292
00:16:13,356 --> 00:16:15,756
Ada lubang di tengahnya.

293
00:16:15,756 --> 00:16:18,756
Potongan bata berserakan

294
00:16:18,756 --> 00:16:22,456
di dekat perbatasan ladang Tn. Nakamura dan Nn. Inoue.

295
00:16:22,456 --> 00:16:23,756
Itu terbang

296
00:16:23,756 --> 00:16:26,456
dan melukai dahi Tn. Nakamura.

297
00:16:26,456 --> 00:16:31,056
Mungkin pecah karena menabrak batu pemisah.

298
00:16:31,056 --> 00:16:34,656
Datang dari mana?

299
00:16:34,656 --> 00:16:36,956
Batu bata itu terbang

300
00:16:36,956 --> 00:16:38,956
